Title: Blossoms of the Past
Description:
With your help, these seeds have grown into magnificent plants. However, the most exciting part is yet to come.

Each of these plant's blossoms contain a treasure trove of information about their history and the magic that binds them to the world tree. By studying these blossoms, we can better understand the lineage of each plant.

Gently collect the blossoms that have fallen and return them to me.
